(138, 11, '_detail', 'In Account Engagement, you can easily create landing pages and publish them without the need for complex integrations or advanced coding. For today\'s challenge you need to create a landing page with a form to promote NextData\'s upcoming product launch event. You are looking to grab interest of your potential prospects who are interested to sign for the event. In future challenges, we will explore various ways to utilize landing pages, so it is important to understand their core functionality.'),
