(142, 12, '_detail', 'Your Day 3 challenge focuses on leveraging the Account Engagement\'s Dynamic Lists and Email Send capabilities. The task is to reach out to trade-show attendees who have expressed interest in seeing the product demo. This is indicated by the \'product_demo_interest\' column being set to \'yes\' in the sample file below and schedule a follow-up email. This task will help you understand how to segment your database in Account Engagement.'),
(143, 12, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
