(282, 127, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">At NextData, the marketing team is looking for a list that displays all event registrations. They are also wondering if it is possible to send a confirmation email to each prospect every time they sign up for an event. Your task is to create a dynamically updating list and send confirmation emails to event registrants.</p>'),
