(351, 163, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">Being aware of prospects\' activities on your website can provide valuable insights and opportunities to take action in a timely manner. Your task today is to create an automation that will notify the prospect owner whenever their prospect visits the event page. Each engagement brings a potential opportunity closer to you!</p>'),
(352, 163, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(353, 163, '_detail', 'In Marketing Cloud Account Engagement, you have the option to create a website tracking code that can be placed on your site to monitor visitor behavior. This allows you to gain visibility into the website visits of individual prospects, including which pages they visit and how often. This information is valuable for understanding their specific needs and interests. To track high-value prospects automatically, you can use a page action that triggers when a prospect visits the event page and notifies the Marketing team.'),
(354, 163, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(355, 163, '_resources', '<p>You can make use of the existing landing page that you created for the product launch event in the previous challenges. If you are still searching for the layout template, you can access it below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-event-promotion.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ae30-02-lp-nextdata-event-promotion-1.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/AE30-02-LT-Event-Promotion.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-02-lp-nextdata-event-promotion\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">üîç Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
