(609, 366, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">At NextData, the marketing team is curious to know how many people intend to attend the event. Today, your task is to send a final reminder to all registrants and kindly ask them to confirm their attendance by clicking on a link provided in the email and capture these individuals in a list. This not only helps boost event attendance but also provides valuable insights for your team to run successful events.</p>'),
(610, 366, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(611, 366, '_detail', 'On Day 8, your task will be to send a final reminder to event registrants. In the reminder email, be sure to include a custom redirect for registrants to confirm their attendance. Also, make sure to add these individuals to a separate list as a step in the process. This step is crucial for NextData to have a clear understanding of the expected event turnout and plan accordingly.'),
(612, 366, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(613, 366, '_resources', '<p>Use the content below to craft your final reminder email. You also need to create a custom confirmation page that will be shown when a user clicks on the custom redirect link.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<!-- Templates -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<!-- Templates: 1st Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/em-event-confirmation.png\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/em-event-confirmation.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1 mx-auto\">\r\n		</a>	\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-08-em-event-confirmation.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-08-em-event-confirmation\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">üîç Email Preview</a></div>	\r\n	</div> \r\n	\r\n	<!-- Templates: 2nd Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lp-event-confirmation.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/lp-event-confirmation.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-08-lt-event-confirmation.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-08-lp-nextdata-event-confirmation\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">üîç Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div> 	\r\n</div>'),
