(712, 392, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData\'s recent product launch event has wrapped up, and you now have a new list of attendees. Your assignment is to develop a nurture program for potential prospects and send them a sequence of emails to continue the engagement.</p>'),
(713, 392, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(714, 392, '_detail', 'On Day 11, your task is to nurture event attendees by creating an Engagement Studio program. This includes importing event attendees, creating three email templates, and building an Engagement Studio program to nurture event attendees into qualified prospects. You also need to ensure that these prospects continue to receive emails until they are assigned to a member of NextData\'s sales team.'),
