(741, 398, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">The marketing team at NextData aims to promote the upcoming research page and target prospects who are likely to engage with the content. Your task today is to create a dynamic list that specifically targets these prospects by leveraging EEF and send them a promotional email.</p>'),
(742, 398, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(743, 398, '_detail', 'For Day 12 of the MCAE30 challenge, your task is to create a dynamic list that captures on-target prospects who are more likely to engage with your next email. To accomplish this, you will use Einstein Engagement Frequency as part of your dynamic list criteria.'),
(744, 398, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(745, 398, '_resources', '<p>While this challenge is about creating a dynamic list, it\'s also a good opportunity to practice creating another list for emails.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-12-email.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-12-email.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-12-em-paper-promote.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-day-12-email-preview\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">üîç Email Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
