(821, 414, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextMobile is getting ready for its monthly customer newsletter, and the marketing team needs a list of customer users with their email addresses, first names, and last names from the primary database. As a member of the marketing team, your responsibility is to extract this data from the database and send it to the marketing team.</p>'),
