(871, 419, '_detail', '<p>You\'ve earned the Explorer Badge in the Account Engagement challenge! This badge symbolizes your growing expertise and readiness to delve deeper into the world of marketing automation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"text-primary mb-4\">Badge Details</h3>\r\n\r\n<h5>Earning Criteria</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>In earning the Explorer badge, participants have mastered the fundamentals of Account Engagement over the first seven days. This journey involved importing prospect lists, creating engaging emails and landing pages, and initiating their first steps in A/B testing. Through these tasks, participants have not only grasped the essentials of email marketing within Account Engagement but also laid a solid foundation for more complex marketing strategies, setting the stage for further exploration and skill development in the world of digital marketing.</p>'),
