(900, 435, '__links', 'field_64dd1a2199239'),
(901, 435, '_solution', '<p>Understanding prospects\' preferences is important because it helps you allocate your resources more effectively. By using Page Actions, you can directly monitor interactions. Additionally, Scoring Categories allow you to accurately categorize the level of engagement. This approach enables you to better segment your database and provide visibility to your Sales team in CRM.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Step-by-step Guide</h5>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"badge text-bg-secondary\">1</span> First, before using Scoring Categories in any automation, you need to add scoring categories. Follow the how-to guide to create your scoring categories. For this challenge, you will create two categories: one for Data Analytics and one for Data Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-15-scoring-categories.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-15-scoring-categories.png\" alt=\"Scoring Categories\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n[guide id=\"438\" status=\"closed\"]\r\n\r\n<p class=\"mt-3\"><span class=\"badge text-bg-secondary\">2</span> Next, create two page actions to track each of the demo request pages. You can customize the Page Score that will be assigned whenever a prospect visits one of the demo request pages.</p> \r\n<p>While the use case for the demo request pages may appear simple, you can gather valuable insights from prospects when they visit multiple pages on your website. The Scoring Category can also be visible in Salesforce, allowing your Sales team to understand prospects\' interests before reaching out to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-15-page-action.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-15-page-action.png\" alt=\"Page Action\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n[guide id=\"223\" status=\"closed\"]\r\n\r\n'),
