(961, 451, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData wants to gather more information from prospects who interact with their content. Your task is to enable progressive profiling on the form for the research paper and ask people to share their challenges with data analysis. This additional section will only be shown if individuals provide their company name.</p>'),
