(1050, 474, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">The marketing team at NextData wants the sales team to promptly follow up with potential prospects. Your task is to identify prospects who are actively engaged and have accumulated at least 30 points. Then, create an automation that identifies these prospects and assigns them to a Salesforce queue.</p>'),
(1051, 474, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1052, 474, '_detail', 'In Day 20 of our journey, you are challenged to create an automation  identifies highly engaged prospects, i.e., those with at least 30 points, and assigns them to a Salesforce queue. It\'s a crucial task that helps NextData streamline its lead lifecycle process and focus on the prospects that matter most. '),
