(1058, 474, '_solution', '<p>Identifying high-value prospects and routing them in a timely manner is crucial for the sales team. By creating an automation rule, you can effectively streamline a manual process, saving time and ensuring that high-potential leads are not overlooked.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Step-by-step Guide</h5>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"badge text-bg-secondary\">1</span> The main objective of today\'s challenge is to manage leads and assign qualified leads to the Sales team. There are multiple methods for passing leads to Salesforce. You can assign them to a user, a user group, or a queue.</p>\r\n<p>For this challenge, you will assign qualified leads to a Salesforce queue. To check the existing queues in Account Engagement, navigate to User Management &gt; Users and click on <strong>View Queues</strong>. If you do not see any queues, you will need to create one by clicking <strong>+ Add Queue</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-20-view-queue.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-20-view-queue.png\" alt=\"Viewing Queue\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"mt-3\"><span class=\"badge text-bg-secondary\">2</span> Once you have confirmed that the queue has been created, you can set up an automation that automatically assigns prospects once they reach 30 points. To do this, you can use an Automation Rule in Account Engagement. In the Rules section, check if the prospect\'s assignment status is <strong>not assigned</strong> and their prospect score is <strong>greater than 29</strong>. In the Actions section, assign the prospect to the queue created in Step 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-20-automation.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-20-automation.png\" alt=\"Automation Setup\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n[guide id=\"403\" status=\"closed\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n'),
