(1138, 502, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData aims to provide personalized attention to every potential prospect, including those who may not be ready to make a purchase yet. As a marketer, your task is to develop an Engagement Studio program that specifically focuses on these prospects. </p>'),
(1139, 502, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1140, 502, '_detail', 'On Day 22, the focus is on nurturing prospects who are not yet ready to make a purchase. Your task is to create an Engagement Studio program that targets these potential customers, using both Engagement Studio and the Lead Lifecycle concept. Identify prospects who are not qualified, meaning they have not reached a score of 30, and send them a series of emails.'),
(1141, 502, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1142, 502, '_resources', '<p>Check out the email copies below to create your version email templates to be used in the nurture program.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-12-email.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-12-email.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-22-em-nurture.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-day-22-email-preview-1\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">üîç Email Preview 1</a></div>		\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-day-22-email-preview-2\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">üîç Email Preview 2</a></div>	\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-day-22-email-preview-3\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">üîç Email Preview 3</a></div>			\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
