(1192, 509, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData is interested in understanding customer communication preferences in their products, as well as the type of marketing content customers would like to receive. As a marketer, your task is to create a preference center for customers to capture this information.</p>'),
(1193, 509, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1194, 509, '_detail', 'On Day 24, our focus will be on personalizing communication settings and understanding the type of marketing materials that customers prefer. Your task is to create a preference center using the built-in options available in Account Engagement. This preference center will allow customers to specify their interests in NextData solutions and indicate their preference for receiving emails about Events, Monthly Newsletter, or Product Updates. By doing so, we can enhance the customer experience and gain valuable insights into our audience.'),
(1195, 509, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1196, 509, '_resources', '<p>The layout template for your preference center will differ slightly from your regular landing pages. Before creating the new preference center, you need to import the provided layout template below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-24-lp.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-24-lp.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-24-lt-preference-center.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/customer-preference-center?epc_hash=KzCOfiHKTeQZd9luXveUGJZGX6IMKpjJYa32WwPFg58\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">üîç Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>	'),
