(1223, 514, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData is once again seeking your assistance after seeing the success of your work on the customer preference center. This time, your assignment is to improve the default unsubscribe page. The goal is to make it more user-friendly and enable a two-click unsubscribe process to prevent automated email security scanners from unsubscribing potential prospects.</p>'),
(1224, 514, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1225, 514, '_detail', 'On Day 25, your task at NextData is to improve the unsubscribe journey, which is a crucial part of the user experience. By enhancing the default page and implementing a two-click unsubscribe process, you can make sure that even users who choose to unsubscribe feel appreciated and heard. '),
(1226, 514, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1227, 514, '_resources', '<p>To enhance the visual appeal of the unsubscribe page, you can utilize the layout template from the previous challenge. Feel free to revise the text on the page as you see fit. Crafting compelling content can help discourage users from unsubscribing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-25-unsubscribe.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-25-unsubscribe.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-25-lt-unsubscribe.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">‚¨áÔ∏è Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/customer-preference-center?epc_hash=KzCOfiHKTeQZd9luXveUGJZGX6IMKpjJYa32WwPFg58\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">üîç Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>	'),
