(1290, 526, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">At NextData, the first experience for new customers is crucial. Your task is to create a welcome email that offers them the option to choose their onboarding experience. This not only facilitates the early adoption of NextData services but also provides valuable insights for future communications.</p>'),
(1291, 526, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1292, 526, '_detail', 'Today, your task is to create a welcome email for NextData\'s new customers. This email should direct them to a custom preference center, where they can select their onboarding preferences. By doing so, we can determine which emails they should receive during the onboarding process. This challenge will help you learn how to create visually appealing forms and effectively utilize data from these customer journeys in your campaigns.'),
