(1365, 545, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData aims to send renewal reminder emails to customers before their contract expires, ensuring they are aware of the expiration and can make informed decisions about renewing. Your challenge is to automate this process, using these emails to gently remind customers and showcase any new features or upgrades available.</p>'),
(1366, 545, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1367, 545, '_detail', 'On the last day of MCAE30, your goal is to improve NextData\'s customer engagement efforts. To achieve this, you will be responsible for implementing a process that effectively engages customers and ensures their continued loyalty. Your key task is to create an engagement studio program that sends a renewal reminder email 30, 15, and 1 day prior to a customer\'s contract expiration. '),
