(1666, 665, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextMobile is preparing for their annual bonus redemption event. During this event, customers can convert their loyalty points at a rate of 1.5 times their current points. The marketing team wants to identify customers who, after applying this bonus conversion rate, will have 150,000 points or more.</p>'),
(1667, 665, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1668, 665, '_detail', 'Challenge yourself to further explore arithmetic operators. Your goal is to apply a 1.5x conversion rate to each customer\'s points and find those who will have 150,000 or more points. Use multiplication to adjust customer points and the <code>‚â•</code> operator to filter the results.'),
