(1869, 680, '_description', '<div>\r\n<p>NextMobile offers a range of mobile plans. For an upcoming campaign, they would like to categorize users based on their monthly usage. The criteria are as follows:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Heavy users: Use more than 50GB</li>\r\n<li>Moderate users: Use more than 25GB</li>\r\n<li>Light users: Use less than 25GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Your task is to classify users based on these criteria, but exclude those who haven\'t used any data.</p>\r\n</div>'),
