(2021, 704, '_detail', 'Today\'s challenge on Day 16 is to use SQL to find the minimum and maximum order amounts for each month. This exercise will involve using functions such as <code>MIN</code> and <code>MAX</code> to discover the range of monthly sales. These insights will be valuable for strategic marketing planning.'),
