(2097, 708, '_detail', 'For today\'s challenge, think about how you can use <code>DATEADD</code> and <code>DATEDIFF</code> together to calculate a future date from a past one. Keep in mind that DATEDIFF finds the number of years since the launch date, while <code>DATEADD</code> uses this interval to project into the future and determine the next renewal date.'),
