(78, 1, '2023-09-11 10:34:13', '2023-09-11 10:34:13', '<strong>Step 1: List Email prerequisites</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>To send a list email, you will need a recipient list, a template, and the content that you will use to update the email.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Navigate to Account Engagement Emails</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Account Engagement Email</strong> > <strong>Drafts</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-1a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-1a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Create a new draft email</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click on <strong>+Send New List Email</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-2-1-detail.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-2-1-detail.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Add email information</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Please fill in the necessary information for the email and attach it to the appropriate folder and campaign. Then, click on <strong>Save</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-2-2-detail.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-2-2-detail.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Choose and apply an email template</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Select a template for your email and apply it.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-3-detail.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-3-detail.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 6: Update the email copy</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click on the <strong>Editor</strong> tab to edit the content of your email. Don\'t forget to create a text version of your email and update the subject line. Click <strong>Save</strong> and go to the <strong>Testing</strong> tab to test your email.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-4-detail.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-4-detail.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 7: Test your email</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click <strong>+New Render</strong> to preview your email in different email clients. You can also send a test email to verify that the email appears as expected.</li>\r\n  <li>Continue to the <strong>Sending</strong> tab to send your email.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-5-detail.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-5-detail.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 8: Prepare your email for sending</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Lists (Send To):</strong> Select at least one recipient list. If needed, you can also choose a suppression list.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Sender:</strong> Choose the email address from which the email will be sent. This address will appear as the \'From\' address in the recipient\'s inbox.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Send or Schedule:</strong> You can either send the email right away or schedule it to be sent at a later date and time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-8a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-email-8a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to send a list email', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-send-a-list-email-in-account-engagement', '', '', '2023-11-13 23:29:13', '2023-11-13 23:29:13', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=78', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
