(199, 1, '2023-11-14 00:23:23', '2023-11-14 00:23:23', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Landing Pages</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Content</strong> > <strong>Landing Pages</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-landing-page-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-landing-page-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Landing Page</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>At the top right corner, you will see the <strong>+ Add Landing Page</strong> button. Click on it to start creating the landing page.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/8e743f99-a091-44b8-9d85-2820a38bc936/create-landing-page-2.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/8e743f99-a091-44b8-9d85-2820a38bc936/create-landing-page-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Input Landing Page Details</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Name</strong>: Enter a name for your landing page. This name will only be used internally.</li>\n  <li><strong>Title</strong>: This will be displayed in the browser\'s title bar when visitors access the page.</li>\n  <li><strong>Description</strong>: This is not visible to end-users and helps search engines understand the context of your landing page.</li>\n  <li><strong>Campaign</strong>: Any metrics related to this campaign will be tracked.</li>\n  <li>After filling out these fields, click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/cf8ed278-fa60-4513-9e8d-afeaee91a800/publish-lp-2-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/cf8ed278-fa60-4513-9e8d-afeaee91a800/publish-lp-2-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Choose a Form for Your Landing Page</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Select <strong>Use Existing Form</strong> and choose the form you would like to use.</li>\n  <li>Proceed by clicking <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/ccd115da-2723-4dc5-a39d-c14c64ca3abd/publish-lp-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/ccd115da-2723-4dc5-a39d-c14c64ca3abd/publish-lp-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 4: Design Your Landing Page</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Select a content layout that match your campaign.</li>\n  <li>Click <strong>Next</strong> to finalize your design.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/fb40da26-bbe7-4486-b530-2e01fd269cd4/publish-lp-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/fb40da26-bbe7-4486-b530-2e01fd269cd4/publish-lp-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 5: Update Landing Page Content</strong> \n<ul>\n  <li>Use the editor to personalize your page. Update the copy per your needs and make necessary updates.</li>\n  <li>Click <strong>Next</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/b98494ad-45d5-49cb-a634-07a912a30789/publish-lp-5a.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/b98494ad-45d5-49cb-a634-07a912a30789/publish-lp-5a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 6: Publish the Landing Page</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preview the landing page and check all the details.</li>\n  <li>Once satisfied, click <strong>Confirm & Save</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/02822369-3014-4003-b42b-66c28c4f8e9b/publish-lp-6-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/02822369-3014-4003-b42b-66c28c4f8e9b/publish-lp-6-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n', 'How to publish a landing page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '108-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-11-14 00:23:23', '2023-11-14 00:23:23', '', 108, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?p=199', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
