(295, 1, '2023-11-20 17:09:26', '2023-11-20 17:09:26', '<div class=\"bg-primary bg-lines-sm py-4\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row py-5\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-8 offset-md-2\">\n				<h1 class=\"fs-2 text-white fw-light text-center mb-0\">\n					Learn Salesforce Marketing Cloud through practical challenges.\n				</h1>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"py-4\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row pt-5\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-8 offset-md-2\">\n				<h2 class=\"fs-3 text-primary\">\n					What is MarketingCloud30?\n				</h2>\n				<p class=\"fs-5\">\n					MarketingCloud30 provides free 30-day challenges on Salesforce Marketing Cloud platforms, such as Marketing Cloud Engagement, Account Engagement, Data Cloud, as well as topics like AMPscript, SSJS, and SQL. The goal is to help marketers to learn new skills through practical scenarios. Each challenge has been carefully crafted and covers both fundamental and advanced scenarios.\n				</p>				\n			</div><!-- col -->\n		</div><!-- row -->	\n		<div class=\"row mt-3\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-8 offset-md-2\">\n				<div class=\"row p-5 bg-light rounded-5\">\n						<h2 class=\"fs-3 text-primary\">\n							Meet Sabuhi üëã\n						</h2>\n					<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n						<p class=\"fs-5\">\n							Hello! I\'m Sabuhi, the creator of MarketingCloud30. With 15 years of experience in marketing automation and Revenue Operations (RevOps), I noticed a gap: the lack of practical scenarios for marketers to effectively apply their knowledge. This gap is particularly noticeable for those transitioning from different fields into the world of marketing automation.\n						</p>\n						<p class=\"fs-5\">\n							To address this issue, I initially started AMPscript30.com and received a lot of requests asking for additional challenges. I recognized the need for a larger platform that could accommodate various challenges, which led me to create marketingcloud30.com. \n						</p>				\n						<p class=\"fs-5 mb-0\">\n							With the launch of this new website, my goal is to not only assist those who want to enhance their skills in Marketing Cloud but also provide them with opportunities to acquire new skills. By offering a diverse range of challenges, tutorials, and resources, I aim to create an environment where users can continuously learn and grow in their Marketing Cloud journey. Whether you are a beginner looking to get started or an experienced professional seeking to expand your knowledge, <span class=\"text-primary fw-semibold\">MarketingCloud30</span> is here to support you every step of the way.\n						</p>\n					</div><!-- col -->\n					<div class=\"col-md-4\">\n						<div><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sabuhiy.png\" class=\"img-fluid rounded-4\"></div>\n						<div class=\"d-grid gap-2 mt-3\">\n							  <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabuhiy/\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Let\'s Connect <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"bi bi-linkedin text-secondary\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n		  <path d=\"M0 1.146C0 .513.526 0 1.175 0h13.65C15.474 0 16 .513 16 1.146v13.708c0 .633-.526 1.146-1.175 1.146H1.175C.526 16 0 15.487 0 14.854V1.146zm4.943 12.248V6.169H2.542v7.225h2.401zm-1.2-8.212c.837 0 1.358-.554 1.358-1.248-.015-.709-.52-1.248-1.342-1.248-.822 0-1.359.54-1.359 1.248 0 .694.521 1.248 1.327 1.248h.016zm4.908 8.212V9.359c0-.216.016-.432.08-.586.173-.431.568-.878 1.232-.878.869 0 1.216.662 1.216 1.634v3.865h2.401V9.25c0-2.22-1.184-3.252-2.764-3.252-1.274 0-1.845.7-2.165 1.193v.025h-.016a5.54 5.54 0 0 1 .016-.025V6.169h-2.4c.03.678 0 7.225 0 7.225h2.4z\"></path>\n		</svg></a>\n						</div>\n					</div><!-- col -->\n				</div><!-- row -->\n			</div><!-- col -->\n		</div><!-- row -->	\n	</div><!-- container -->	\n</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-11