(375, 1, '2023-11-27 04:57:42', '2023-11-27 04:57:42', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Custom Redirects</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to Content > Custom Redirects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Custom Redirect</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>Add Custom Redirect</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-2.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Add Custom Redirect Details</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Name</strong>: Provide a descriptive name for the custom redirect.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Folder</strong>: Choose a relevant folder to organize the custom redirects.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Tags (optional)</strong>: You can add specific tags to further categorize and segment your custom redirects.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Campaign</strong>: Select the appropriate campaign to associate with this custom redirect.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Destination URL</strong>: This is the URL where users will be redirected when they click on the custom redirect link.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Tracker Domain</strong>: If you have multiple domains, choose the one that aligns with your campaign.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Vanity URL (optional)</strong>: Enter a unique path for the asset or leave it blank to use an autogenerated URL.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-3.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/custom-redirect-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Create Custom Redirect</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Once you have filled out all the necessary fields and details, click the <strong>Create Custom Redirect</strong> button to complete the process.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'How to create a custom redirect', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-a-custom-redirect', '', '', '2023-11-27 04:59:31', '2023-11-27 04:59:31', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=375', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
