(381, 1, '2023-11-28 11:46:05', '2023-11-28 11:46:05', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Dynamic Content</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Content</strong> > <strong>Dynamic Content</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Dynamic Content</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>+Add Dynamic Content</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-2.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Add New Dynamic Content</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Name</strong>: Provide a descriptive name.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Folder</strong>: Select a folder to save the dynamic content in.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Default Content</strong>: This content is displayed when the viewer is not a prospect or when no variations match.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Variations</strong>: Choose a field that will be used as criteria for the remaining variations.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Variation N</strong>: Reference the field and build the logic accordingly.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-3.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Preview Dynamic Content</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>After saving, click on the Testing Tools button to preview the dynamic content and ensure that it appears as intended.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-4.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dynamic-content-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to create a dynamic content', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-a-dynamic-content', '', '', '2023-11-28 11:46:05', '2023-11-28 11:46:05', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=381', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
