(403, 1, '2023-12-03 08:36:05', '2023-12-03 08:36:05', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Automation Rules</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Automations</strong> > <strong>Automation Rules</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Create a New Rule</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>+Add Automation Rule</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-2.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Set Up Basic Information</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Enter a name for your automation rule.</li>\r\n  <li>Optionally, provide a description.</li>\r\n  <li>Choose the folder where you want to save the rule.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Define Rule Criteria</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click on +<strong>Add New Rule</strong> to set the conditions for the rule.</li>\r\n  <li>You can select criteria such as prospect field values, page views, form submissions, and more.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-4.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Choose Actions</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>After setting your criteria, click on +<strong>Add New Action</strong>.</li>\r\n  <li>Select the actions that should be triggered when the criteria are met. Actions can include changing a prospect\'s score, adding them to a list, sending an email, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-5.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 6: Enable the Rule</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>After configuring the rule, click on <strong>Create automation rules</strong>.</li>\r\n  <li>The automation rules are created in a Paused state. Click on the <strong>Resume automation rules</strong> link to activate the automation rule.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-6.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-rule-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to create an automation rule', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-an-automation-rule', '', '', '2023-12-03 08:36:05', '2023-12-03 08:36:05', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=403', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
