(493, 1, '2023-12-11 15:11:40', '2023-12-11 15:11:40', '<strong>Step 1: Access Campaigns in Salesforce</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Log into your Salesforce account. Navigate to the <strong>App Launcher</strong> (grid icon), and select <strong>Campaigns</strong> from the list of available options.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Placeholder for Screenshot -->\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-campaign-1.png\"><img src=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\" alt=\"Access Campaigns in Salesforce\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Create a New Campaign</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Inside the Campaigns module, click on the <strong>New</strong> button to start creating a new campaign.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Placeholder for Screenshot -->\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\"><img src=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\" alt=\"Create New Campaign\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Enter Campaign Details</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fill in the necessary information such as <strong>Campaign Name</strong>, <strong>Type</strong>, <strong>Start Date</strong>, <strong>End Date</strong>, and any other relevant details.</li>\n  <li>You can also set the campaign\'s <strong>Status</strong> and assign it to a specific <strong>Campaign Hierarchy</strong> if needed.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Placeholder for Screenshot -->\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\"><img src=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\" alt=\"Enter Campaign Details\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 4: Save and Launch the Campaign</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Once all the details are entered, click on the <strong>Save</strong> button to create the campaign.</li>\n  <li>Your campaign is now ready and can be included in your marketing and sales initiatives.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<!-- Placeholder for Screenshot -->\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\"><img src=\"YOUR_SCREENSHOT_URL\" alt=\"Save and Launch Campaign\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n', 'How to create a Salesforce campaign', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '487-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-12-11 15:11:40', '2023-12-11 15:11:40', '', 487, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?p=493', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(494, 1, '2023-12-11 19:37:48', '2023-12-11 19:37:48', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Engagement Studio</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Automations</strong> > <strong>Engagement Studio</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Engagement Program</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>+ Add Engagement Program</strong> button to start creating a new ESP.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-2.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Input Details and Save</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Name</strong>: Assign a name for internal use in Account Engagement to organize assets.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Folder</strong>: Select a folder for storing the engagement program.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Description</strong>: Provide a description for internal reference.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Recipient List</strong>: Define the audience for the Engagement Studio program.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Suppression List</strong>: Optionally, exclude individuals who don\'t meet entry criteria.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Send Time</strong>: Configure the email delivery time, including time zone and weekday.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-3.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Build an Engagement Studio Program</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Engagement programs consist of three types of steps: trigger steps, rule steps, and action steps.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Triggers:</strong> Set up Triggers to evaluate prospect actions after a specific period.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-1-trigger.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-1-trigger.png\" alt=\"Triggers\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Rules:</strong> Use Rules to direct prospects along paths based on certain conditions or data.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-2-rule.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-2-rule.png\" alt=\"Rules\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Actions:</strong> Choose Actions based on the journey your prospects take.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-3-action.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-4-3-action.png\" alt=\"Actions\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Test and Send</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Utilize the testing feature in Engagement Studio to verify your program functions as expected.</li>\r\n  <li>Start your engagement program by clicking <strong>Start</strong> or schedule it for a future date.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-5.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/create-esp-5.png\" alt=\"Test and Send\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to create an engagement studio program', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-an-engagement-studio-program', '', '', '2023-12-11 19:37:48', '2023-12-11 19:37:48', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=494', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
