(743, 2, '2025-06-09 14:45:50', '2025-06-09 14:45:50', '<div class=\"bg-secondary content-space-t-3 content-space-t-md-4 content-space-b-1 content-space-b-md-3 overflow-hidden\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-10\">\n			<h1 class=\"fs-2 text-white mb-0 fw-normal\">Learn <span class=\"fw-semibold\">Salesforce Marketing Cloud</span> through practical challenges.</h1>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n<!-- SVG Elements -->\n	<div class=\"zi-0 graphic-dots\">\n		[theme_embed_svg svg=\"/assets/images/hero-dots.svg\"]\n			</div>\n	<div class=\"zi-0 graphic-icons\">\n		[theme_embed_svg svg=\"/assets/images/hero-icons.svg\"]\n			</div>\n	<!-- SVG Elements -->\n</div>\n<!-- bg-secondary -->\n\n<div class=\"container content-space-t-2 content-space-b-2\">\n	<h2 class=\"fs-3 fw-normal\">What is MarketingCloud30?</h2>\n	<p>MarketingCloud30 provides free 30-day challenges on Salesforce Marketing Cloud platforms, such as Marketing Cloud Engagement, Account Engagement, Data Cloud, as well as topics like AMPscript, SSJS, and SQL. The goal is to help marketers to learn new skills through practical scenarios. Each challenge has been carefully crafted and covers both fundamental and advanced scenarios.</p>\n</div><!-- container -->\n\n<div class=\"bg-light content-space-t-2 content-space-b-2\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row g-5\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-4\">\n				<div><img class=\"img-fluid rounded-4\" src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/sabuhiy.png\" /></div>\n				<div class=\"d-grid gap-2 mt-3\"><a class=\"btn btn-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabuhiy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"\"><i class=\"bi bi-linkedin\"></i> Let\'s Connect</a></div>\n			</div>\n			<!-- col -->\n					\n			<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n				<h2 class=\"fs-3 fw-normal\">Meet Sabuhi üëã</h2>\n				<p>Hello! I\'m Sabuhi, the creator of MarketingCloud30. With 15 years of experience in marketing automa